00:41:37.344 --> 00:41:39.164
context of the NOD

711
00:41:41.804 --> 00:41:44.044
mouse model of autoimmune diabetes. Excuse me.

712
00:41:44.124 --> 00:41:48.104
This is a mouse model that we know if we give PD-1 inhibitors, we get accelerated

